data.name: HelpButton.ToolTip
data.value: Links: - Shows links to synchronous classes - Does not fetch from KHub (you must add your own) - Choose the day of the week in the drop down list Add Link: - Add a link for a synchronous class Enable Button: - Enables automatic opening of links when its almost time Disable Button: - Disable automatic opening of links Calendar: - Takes you to the Calendar View To-do: - Takes you to the To-do List
